{"tid":2118811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"波蘭總理暗示會跟隨美國 不會使用華為5G","createTime":"2020-07-21T16:53:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T06:12:56.000Z","uid":28114,"like":148,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"864411a6ee2d69f54027265604a63e1e68404da1","tid":2118811,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:53:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/secpompeo/status/1285268834807697408?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsecpompeo%2Fstatus%2F1285268834807697408%3Fs%3D21&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=de24b9eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsecpompeo%2Fstatus%2F1285268834807697408%3Fs%3D21&h=be1d071f\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/secpompeo/status/1285268834807697408?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nArticle of the Prime Minister of the Republic of Poland Mateusz Morawiecki in the Daily Telegraph on 5G<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.pl/web/sweden/article-of-the-prime-minister-of-the-republic-of-poland-mateusz-morawiecki-in-the-daily-telegraph-on-5g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.pl%2Fweb%2Fsweden%2Farticle-of-the-prime-minister-of-the-republic-of-poland-mateusz-morawiecki-in-the-daily-telegraph-on-5g&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=ae3eb67d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.pl/web/sweden/article-of-the-prime-minister-of-the-republic-of-poland-mateusz-morawiecki-in-the-daily-telegraph-on-5g</a>"},{"pid":"f6e6fa92e3da57fe68fe2c436fe187656def83c6","tid":2118811,"uid":28114,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:54:28.000Z","msg":"For Poland, we must ensure that we guard against the risks and vulnerabilities that arise from advances in 5G. We are committed to a 5G ecosystem built on trust, the bedrock of any system that carries our citizens&rsquo; most private information and the fruits of our intellectual property.<br />\n<br />\nWhen building that ecosystem, we are faced with one question: who do we trust? The choices are clear: in Europe, we have two trusted, European vendors, both world-class firms with transparent business practices based on the rule of law. On the other side are two companies controlled by an authoritarian regime. Technological security, just like epidemiological security, is a crucial dimension of national security. <span class=\"red\">Countries must be able to control technology suppliers to ensure safety, which is why they must be from countries that respect our fundamental values: democracy, transparency, human rights, and the rule of law. Otherwise, our control over them will be illusory, and the responsibility for security ill-defined.</span>"},{"pid":"eb40c17de717d3c7ba31d805a3f5ad04c8447b2a","tid":2118811,"uid":270220,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:54:36.000Z","msg":"駐軍波蘭，德國俾支那養。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4923b82db7dd8ac1f1a4101c69978dc56b9fd7","tid":2118811,"uid":254594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"864411a6ee2d69f54027265604a63e1e68404da1","tid":2118811,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:53:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/secpompeo/status/1285268834807697408?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsecpompeo%2Fstatus%2F1285268834807697408%3Fs%3D21&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj3s01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=de24b9eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsecpompeo%2Fstatus%2F1285268834807697408%3Fs%3D21&h=be1d071f\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/secpompeo/status/1285268834807697408?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\nArticle of the Prime Minister of the Republic of Poland Mateusz Morawiecki in the Daily Telegraph on 5G<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.pl/web/sweden/article-of-the-prime-minister-of-the-republic-of-pol